(Corrects battery life of device in second paragraph.)  Amazon.com Inc. Chief Executive
Officer  Jeff Bezos  unveiled a Kindle e-reader with a higher-
resolution screen at an event in Santa Monica, California.  The Kindle Paperwhite e-book reader has light directed
toward the screen, making it work better in direct sunlight,
Bezos said at the event today. The device has battery life of 8
weeks, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
